      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "FIREWALL - Agent (filter/OUTPUT)\n    - DEFAULT: DENY egress\n    - DROP private CIDRs\n    - AGENT_ALLOW / AGENT_BLOCK dynamic chains\n    - CLI can allow/deny hosts and/or CIDRs",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "FIREWALL - Agent (filter/OUTPUT)\n    - DEFAULT: DENY egress\n    - DROP private CIDRs\n    - AGENT_ALLOW / AGENT_BLOCK dynamic chains\n    - CLI can allow/deny hosts and/or CIDRs",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
