      "updated": 1772207713691,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "FIREWALL - NESTED CONTAINERS (mangle/FORWARD)\n\n- DEFAULT: ALLOW egress (opposite of agent)\n- DROP private CIDRs (same set as agent)\n- POD_ALLOW / POD_BLOCK dynamic chains\n- CLI can allow/deny hosts and/or CIDRs",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "FIREWALL - NESTED CONTAINERS (mangle/FORWARD)\n\n- DEFAULT: ALLOW egress (opposite of agent)\n- DROP private CIDRs (same set as agent)\n- POD_ALLOW / POD_BLOCK dynamic chains\n- CLI can allow/deny hosts and/or CIDRs",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
